---
title: Sicilian Caponata with Pine Nuts and Garlic Ciabatta
description: A little bit sweet and a little bit sour, caponata is a famous Sicilian dish made from eggplant, tomatoes, olives, and tangy vinegar. Our version is sweetened up with some roasted red peppers!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/sicilian-caponata-7128f5ab.jpg
